{
    "title": "Knock knock",
    "cards": [{
        "id": 0,
        "text": "",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Did you hear any rumours?",
                "actions": "GOTO 1"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 1,
        "text": "Ahh, PLAYERNAME, i want to welcome you to my little shop! I would be very happy to take measure on your feet, to gift you some fine cardosian shoes!",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Who are you?",
                "actions": "GOTO 2"
            },{
                "text": "Yeah I already know.",
                "actions": "GOTO 0"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 2,
        "text": "I am Derrek, the cardosian Shoemaker. Didnt you hear about my craftsmanship?",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Frankly not.",
                "actions": "GOTO 3"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 3,
        "text": "Well then let me tell you PLAYERNAME, I see a good foot when I look at one and you Sir have an excellent standing.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Sure do!",
                "actions": "GOTO 4"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 4,
        "text": "If you ask me PLAYERNAME, I wouldnt trust those klongons one bit. They all look the same!",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Thats racist Derrek.",
                "actions": "GOTO 5"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 5,
        "text": "I am not saying they ALL look the same. Just these ones.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "What makes you say that?",
                "actions": "GOTO 6"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 6,
        "text": "Look at their feet, PLAYERNAME, their FEET!",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "What about them?",
                "actions": "GOTO 7"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 7,
        "text": "Are you familiar with the story about the two pillars in front of the Riverpalace?",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Not particularly.",
                "actions": "GOTO 8"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 8,
        "text": "It is an old cardosian bedtime story. Would you like to hear it?",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Go ahead.",
                "actions": "GOTO 9"
            },{
                "text": "Actually, could we just: Shoes.",
                "actions": "GOTO 26"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 9,
        "text": "Well, t´was many lightyears ago in space, when a young girl stood before the riverpalace Knuaq in the providence of Knuaq.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Lightyears are a measure of distance.",
                "actions": "GOTO 20"
            },
            {
                "text": "Mhm.",
                "actions": "GOTO 22"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 20,
        "text": "Back then they werent, PLAYERNAME.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Sure, if you say so.",
                "actions": "GOTO 22"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 22,
        "text": "That young girl had the shiniest scales in all of Cardosia, or as it was called back then Knuaq, the large Knuaq.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Ok.",
                "actions": "GOTO 23"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 23,
        "text": "You see PLAYERNAME, having especially shiny scales is a symbol of great disgrace for my people.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Interesting.",
                "actions": "GOTO 24"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 24,
        "text": "Just as the two pillars next to the river, the girl knew she was nothing more than the mere reflection of a cardosian rat next to the palaces marble walls, shining light on itself through the cracks.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "Im sorry, what?",
                "actions": "GOTO 25"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 25,
        "text": "Dont you understand? Those klongon feet are just like the pillars in the story, dont you think?",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "I see, very helpful, Derrek.",
                "actions": "GOTO 27"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 26,
        "text": "The Klongon´s feet look identical.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "I see, very helpful, Derrek.",
                "actions": "GOTO 27"
            }
        ]
    },{
        "id": 27,
        "text": "I will let you know when your boots are ready, PLAYERNAME.",
        "sprite": "sprDerrek00",
        "answers": [
            {
                "text": "You can reach me through the COM-lines, but stay out of the emergency ones.",
                "actions": "GOTO 0"
            }
        ]
    }]
